{"tid":1579852,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"警方反對周六光復屯門公園遊行","createTime":"2019-09-18T18:55:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-18T19:25:33.000Z","uid":7828,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"64cfd486e382440c0c708b9b3d717e3b5980217d","tid":1579852,"uid":7828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T18:55:46.000Z","msg":"有團體計劃星期六在屯門公園發起遊行，但接獲警方反對通知書，團體決定提出上訴。<br />\n<br />\n發起遊行的屯門公園衛生關注組表示，遊行是為了反映社區訴求，要求當局更有效打擊屯門公園的噪音及涉嫌賣淫的問題。關注組批評警方，在商討期間刻意刁難，目的是打壓集會及表達自由，關注組對警方禁止遊行感到遺憾。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=363255&amp;refer=\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D363255%26refer%3D&d=YpkAIiMN%2BbqadqYnCsWFxqtywrPEU2nSstxgUPIv8k8%3D&h=9480da25\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D363255%26refer%3D&h=52144e63\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=363255&amp;refer=</a>"},{"pid":"9847168cde96ae313d87f63147d69e4faf88335d","tid":1579852,"uid":61416,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T18:59:36.000Z","msg":"其實依家佢乜遊行都反對<br />\n根本剝削緊人權自由<br />\n係咪可以唔洗理/申請司法覆核推翻<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b325693b3e39d0713a9e9c46ae755084331779a9","tid":1579852,"uid":202876,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T19:15:13.000Z","msg":"屯門試過遊行都冇事<br />\n點解上次批今次唔批?<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63180110731f93875ef75860f340c474794cb186","tid":1579852,"uid":14433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T19:17:12.000Z","msg":"其實有邊一次近排嘅遊行活動係佢會同意架呢？好似冇一次得到佢批准囉！所以都係決定唔理佢應該去就照去囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b77fe5abb9570e8966d21bf6d6c07831905ec7d","tid":1579852,"uid":264717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T1